<div class="home-banner">
    <div class="home-banner-content">
        <h6 class="sub-title">
            PERFORMANCE SKINCARE
            <span class="mobile-hide">MADE SIMPLE.</span>
        </h6>
        <h1 class="title">How To Use
            <br>
            The Good</h1>
        <p class="para">One simple step. Every night. Balancing for oily skin. Nourishing for dry skin. Proven performance for everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-banner-img">
        <img src="{{"right-hero-image.png" | asset_url }}" alt="">
    </div>
</div>

<div class="how-to-use">
    <div class="how-to-use-content">
        <div class="how-to-use_item">
            <img class="how-touse-icon" src="{{ "cleanseer_icon.svg" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>Cleanse and thoroughly dry your face.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-to-use_item">
            <img class="how-touse-icon" src="{{ "serum_icon.svg" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>Press the top down to fill the dropper (it’ll only fill ⅓).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-to-use_item">
            <img class="how-touse-icon" src="{{ "dropper_icon.svg" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>Unscrew the top and press down again to release the serum into your palm.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-to-use_item">
            <img class="how-touse-icon" src="{{ "face_icon.svg" | asset_url }}" alt="face icon"/>
            <p>Gently massage the serum onto your face and neck.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-to-use-center">
        <p>The Good is lightweight and designed to absorb quickly, so you’ll never feel greasy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="how-to-use-video">

        <video muted poster="{{ "howtousevideo.png" | asset_url }}" onclick="this.paused ? this.play() : this.pause();">
            <source src="http://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/ElephantsDream.mp4" type="video/mp4">

        </video>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="testimonials-wrapper">
