            <span class="">ADAM SCHAFER, HOST OF MIND PUMP PODCAST</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-slider">
        <div class="testimonials-slider-item">
            <img src="{{ "headshot.png" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>“Great feel to this product, no oily greasy feel to your skin after applying it.”</p>
            <span>
                Jon, 42 | Los Angeles, CA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-slider-item">
            <img src="{{ "headshot.png" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>“Application could not be more simple. Wash your face and then apply [The Good]. Absorbs quickly. Go to sleep. Wake up younger looking.”
            </p>
            <span>
                Jon, 42 | Los Angeles, CA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-slider-item">
            <img src="{{ "headshot.png" | asset_url }}" alt=""/>
            <p>“I have dry skin and eczema. [But with The Good], my face is fresher, healthier, more hydrated. Results are quite astounding.”</p>
            <span>
                Jon, 42 | Los Angeles, CA</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="result-section">
    <div class="result-content">
        <h1 class="title">
            How Can One Serum Deliver Results For All Skin Types?</h1>
        <div class="result-qa-item">
            <h4 class="sub-title">
                1. FORMULATED FOR THE MICROBIOME.</h4>
            <p class="para">By acting on your skin’s microbiome, The Good's prebiotic and antioxidant functions help your skin find its unique equilibrium.</p>

        </div>
        <div class="result-qa-item">
            <h4 class="sub-title">
                2. OIL-BALANCING.
            </h4>
            <p class="para">This non-comedogenic (won’t clog pores) serum includes wild bergamot and frankincense, which adapt to your skin, moisturizing or balancing only where you need it.</p>

        </div>
        <div class="result-qa-item">
            <h4 class="sub-title">
                3. SKIN-MIMICKING.
            </h4>
            <p class="para">27 botanicals work synergistically to mirror skin’s natural processes and sebum structure, so your skin readily absorbs the nutrients from our wild antioxidant complex.</p>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="result-img">
        <span class="verticle-text">LOREM IPUM</span>
        <img src="{{ "result-img.png" | asset_url }}" alt="">
    </div>
</div>

